<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:orientation="vertical"
    android:background="@drawable/home"
    tools:context="com.albaincompaniesltd.application.thetruemeaningofislam.org.albaincompaniesltd.application.thetruemeaningofislam.PillarsActivity">

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/txtjihad"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
        android:layout_gravity="center"
        android:layout_marginTop="50dp"
        android:text="What are the pillars of faith?"
        android:textColor="#fff"
        android:textSize="18sp"
        android:textStyle="bold" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView5"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginStart="77dp"
        android:layout_marginTop="150dp" />

    <ScrollView
        android:id="@+id/scroll1"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content">

        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/textView6"
            android:layout_width="320dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:textSize="16sp"
            android:padding="10dp"
            android:layout_gravity="center"
            android:text="1. Believe in Allah

2. Believe in the Angels {e.g Angel Gabriel}

3. Believe in his Books {The book of the prophet David, The book Moses, The book of Jesus and the book of the Prophet Muhamad P.B.U.H}

4. Believe in his Messengers

5. Believe in the day of judgement

6. Believe in Gods plans

It is a requirement as a Muslim to know and honour Allah even if you cannot see or hear him. As a Muslim you must have knowledge of Allah, knowledge of your religion and its requirements and knowledge of the prophets {Peace be upon them}



"
            android:textColor="#fff"
            android:maxLines="10"
            android:minLines="1"
            android:ellipsize="end"
            android:scrollbars="vertical"
            />



    </ScrollView>


    <Button
        android:id="@+id/btnFromFaith"
        android:layout_width="300dp"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginLeft="40dp"
        android:background="#EA8B0F"
        android:onClick="FromFaith"
        android:gravity="center"
        android:text="Next Lesson"
        android:textColor="#fff" />

    <Button
        android:id="@+id/btnListenFaith"
        android:layout_width="300dp"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginLeft="40dp"
        android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
        android:onClick="faithListen"
        android:background="#EA8B0F"
        android:gravity="center"
        android:text="Listen to Lesson"
        android:textColor="#fff" />


</LinearLayout>
